      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That seems a bit extreme, doesn't it? I'm not talking about getting drunk, just one small glass of wine to take the edge off. I've heard people mix things like this all the time without anything happening. Are you sure it's actually that dangerous if it's just a tiny amount? It feels like it would just make the relaxation effect better.",
