      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what you're saying but it feels like you're being super cautious. i'm an adult and i know my limits. if i just have a really small amount, like half a glass, and i don't do anything else, what's the actual huge risk? it just seems like it would be a way more effective way to get the sleep i need instead of just waiting for the pill to kick in on its own.",
